text: "DAMN." is a Kendrick Lamar album released on April 14, 2017. It was co- produced by Top Dawg Entertainment. This has already surpassed 9.5 billion streams on Spotify. all of the songs include: BLOOD, DNA, YAH, ELEMENT, FEEL, LOYALTY, PRIDE, HUMBLE, LUST, LOVE, XXX, FEAR, GOD, and DUCKWORTH. ==References== Category:2017 albums Category:Kendrick Lamar albums
title: DAMN.
